Class CodeProblem

java.lang.Object
  com.google.inject.tools.suite.snippets.CodeProblem
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
CodeProblem.BadClassProblem, CodeProblem.BindingProblem, CodeProblem.CreationProblem, CodeProblem.InvalidModuleContextProblem, CodeProblem.InvalidModuleProblem
public class CodeProblem
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Represents a problem found involving the user's guice code, such as a CreationException. These are passed to the ProblemsHandler for realtime notification to the user as well as passed along with CodeLocations for display as results.

Author:
Darren Creutz (dcreutz@gmail.com)
